divs: Sighting DetailsAt the time I was going to Tomy's restaurant photographing strange objects in the area (mostly orbs). I was outside of Tomy's restaurant smoking a cigarette. I stepped forward a couple of steps, and looked up. To my right I saw a 1 foot in diameter lighted object. It was 35 feet high, and was traveling towards the main street (Chapman Ave.)at about 3 mph. It was very bright, and I could see it was packed will electrical equipment (components, chips etc.). When it got over the middle of Chapman Ave. it disappeared completely into another dimension. I was amazed by this, and I was prompted to think that the object was some kind of extraterrestrial experiment. Thank you.
